username: user name should not contain whitespaces
password: Min. 8 characters, should include 1 letter and 1 number
orgunit: Use Org Unit ID to avoid errors
teams: Use Team names. Use comma separated values for multiple teams: Team A,Team B
phone_number: The phone number as a string (e.g. +32...)
editable_org_unit_types: Use comma separated Org Unit Type IDs: 1, 2
